     This is QUADRATIC convergence — the hallmark of Newton's method.
     5 steps: ε → (3/2)ε^2 → ... → essentially machine epsilon.

  5. BASIN OF ATTRACTION: σ ∈ (0, √3) for cubic. All singular values
